Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.24,0:00:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeus proclaimed...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.62,0:00:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the human tribes living on the land...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.79,0:00:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,learned to sow the seeds and cultivate the fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karl, your pronunciation is off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.55,0:00:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.09,0:00:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten better, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you first came here...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought, "Such a terrible student\Nhas come to my place."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Japanese doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.23,0:00:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he's traveling around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure would like to meet him again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:31.87,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(225,200)\pos(368,354)}The Real Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.89,0:02:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You started working?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interior decorator.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.15,0:02:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you have an eye for furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I do interior design,\Nit's a little different than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a kitchen coordinator.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never really set foot in a kitchen until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe I should ask you to do my kitchen next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I get the feeling you have expensive tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been drinking, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not a single drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take it slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you try to rush it, today is going to\Npass by and tomorrow will still come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happiness is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.37,0:03:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tired of hearing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that knowing I was waiting for him at the\Ntrain station was enough to make him happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man., Martin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are so strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness keeps fading away...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and only happy memories remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People sure have a convenient makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we can keep on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mr. Verdeman, the attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who cleared the suspicions against you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned everything I could about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came from Kinderheim 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A member of East German intelligence,\Nyou masqueraded as a journalist...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and traveled around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, as a freelance reporter...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you continued to investigate human\Nrights violations in old East Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that big bag of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found piles of supporting documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the one thing that remains a mystery...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is your real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolfgang Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left without telling us anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not an inspector anymore, Detective Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you became an instructor at a police academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've begun to talk with my daughter a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only through e-mail, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, we've lived without\Nsaying anything to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lived without knowing anything about each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how many things people can really\Ntell each other while they're alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably had a lot of things\Nyou wanted to talk about...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,over a good beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going back to D{\fnMeiryo U}ü{\fnNarkisim}sseldorf?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The company I have a contract with is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That place has a lot of bad memories for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Trying to run away is useless."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What's important is to face the truth and move forward."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you dispose of this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me immediately if something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Dr. Gillen and I are here to help at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give my regards to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma's hearing continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still unable to grasp the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Lunge begins his testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has this developed into the worst serial\Nmurder case in the history of Europe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma completely exonerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The authorities express their apologies to Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The motive behind the case is still unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the identity of the mysterious\Nyoung man said to be the real culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M{\fnMeiryo U}ü{\fnNarkisim}nster Medical School offers Dr.\NTenma a position as professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma continues to decline the position.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma participates in "Doctors Without Borders."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The articles keep getting smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People have a convenient makeup, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten big since the last time I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten slimier since the last\Ntime I saw you, Mr. Heckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're still as snotty as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm going to soccer practice, so\NI don't have time to hang out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Tenma come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about this "Doctors Without Borders" thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just acting cool and not making any money!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can never get in touch with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do if he came back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took a job he asked me to do a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After thinking about the expenses and the labor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the reward he offered wasn't nearly enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma asked you to do something for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He only asked me to find someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I had a hell of a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even went so far as to steal top\Nsecret material from the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what will happen if they catch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give this invoice to Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him that if he can't pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make him work as an underground doctor again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:20.78,Name,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(255,100)\pos(352,385)}Southern France
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't seen you in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I had to go abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please share this with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What nice weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All these leaves are photosynthesizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless genes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about Mendel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who determined the laws of inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the same college as Mendel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brno University.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A town in Moravia in southeastern Czechoslovakia, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wonderful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely go there next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for coming here so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For allowing me to have such a wonderful time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel quite well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I can talk about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how frightening it may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have something you want to ask me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the mother of the twins, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was killed by that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing him was that man's experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I died...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the children that were growing inside of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would surely deliver punishment to that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't let go of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is the real monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the children alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will probably never recall this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave those children names.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their names are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still the tardy offender, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're ten minutes late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Professor Kronecker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know why you've been called here today, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's regarding your graduation thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yesr sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know a lot has happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been hard to catch up on everything\Nafter you took a break from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't excuse my grades...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, about your thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's first class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best thesis paper I've ever seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,out of all the students I've taught.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.53,0:16:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you wish to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To become a lawyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pray that many lives will be saved by your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tardiness won't be allowed in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fraulein Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Dieter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:45.37,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal with your graduation?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:47.37,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you fail, I'm still with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should have you comfort me next time I see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:54.09,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless to fake it, because I can tell by your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:55.01,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:55.71,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:17:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where things start to get tough, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.05,0:17:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't come back right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I have a lot of plans with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:10.65,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:12.56,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma is coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:18.11,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got a call from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:22.24,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,But he said he has to leave again\Nwith Doctors Without Borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:26.50,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'll be back by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:28.16,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,You should hurry up and come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I can't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to see Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.87,0:17:56.55,Name,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(268,200)\pos(355,391)}Bayern State Police Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been asleep since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've spoken with your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She loves you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She told me your real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing I want to ask you, and only you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that monster appeared before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch these children!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to leave one and take the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:20:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, which one will we take?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.00,0:20:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't let go of my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did my mother try to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or did she mistake me for my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was the one she didn't want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.84,0:22:31.01,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,471)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:44.44,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:44.44,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:47.40,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:23:01.08,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:23:01.08,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.68,0:23:25.94,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:34.36,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.36,0:23:36.82,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
